%N A091433 a(n) = 2*3^n - 18*4^n + 24*5^n.
%H A091433 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (12,-47,60).
%F A091433 a(n) = Sum_{i=2..n+2} i!*i^2*Stirling2(n,i-2)*(-1)^(n+2-i).
%F A091433 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, May 08 2026: (Start)
%F A091433 G.f.: 2*(4 - 21*x + 29*x^2)/((1-3*x)*(1-4*x)*(1-5*x)).
%F A091433 E.g.f.: 2*exp(3*x)*(1 - 9*exp(x) + 12*exp(2*x)).
%F A091433 a(n) = 12*a(n-1) - 47*a(n-2) + 60*a(n-3). (End)
